{"tid":135887,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Bill Paxton 過身 享年61","createTime":"2017-02-26T16:09:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T19:34:21.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0266e055d1544d7b0fb6e0b04ca52c4edae28207","tid":135887,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T16:09:26.000Z","msg":"曾演出過《龍捲風》、《鐵達尼號》等知名作品的好萊塢男星比爾派斯頓（Bill Paxton）於美國時間 2 月 25 號在手術過程中引發併發症過世，享壽 61 歲，這位知名演員和億萬導演詹姆斯卡麥隆（James Cameron）多次合作，包括 1984 年的《魔鬼終結者》（The Terminator）、《異形2》（Aliens）、《魔鬼大帝：真實謊言》（True Lies）。<br />\n<br />\n近期比爾最知名的角色可能事由湯姆克魯斯（Tom Cruise）主演的《明日邊界》（Edge of Tmorrow）中的長官一角，生涯雖然並沒有擔任過太多男主角，卻是觀眾印象深刻的配角，他與影后海倫杭特（Helen Hunt）演出的《龍捲風》當年在北美買出超過 2 億的票房，僅次於《ID4星際終結者》（Idependence Day），可能是比爾最成功的作品。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CTeux9pVEAA4cUm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCTeux9pVEAA4cUm.jpg&h=f6edc537&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0ad3a4e7fcb60c4608386357b107b00263d6460","tid":135887,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T16:10:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://nerdist.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/i5EDfFogNb1Fx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnerdist.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F05%2Fi5EDfFogNb1Fx.gif&h=83884c32&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04c5dd97807e7c5c63d9aa95c8f1a90cb953757e","tid":135887,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T16:11:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.movieroomreviews.com/sites/movieroomreviews.com/files/bill-paxton.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.movieroomreviews.com%2Fsites%2Fmovieroomreviews.com%2Ffiles%2Fbill-paxton.jpg&h=c4cf9948&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"788532777f156799fd71904613dae2459ac9d36c","tid":135887,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T16:16:20.000Z","msg":"Rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" cla